data.description: Look no more! Welcome to this beautiful, updated CORNER lot home! Enjoy the comforts of a spacious one car garage and plenty of street parking. Lots of room to park an RV or Boat! You will be greeted with NEW: paint, blinds, electrical panel (2021), and flooring both in the kitchen and living room. The style of the home is a bi-level with an open floor plan paired with a completely rebuilt fireplace. Yes, REBUILT! Three bedrooms on the lower floor with a full bathroom. A full master bedroom and bathroom paired with a balcony upstairs and a loft with potential to become another bedroom or making it a private office! Hot water heater and furnace was installed 2015 (new)! Master bedroom upstairs has a balcony, get a great view of Pikes Peak! Laundry is in the kitchen. MOVE IN READY! NEW PAINT EVERYWHERE! Two parks within walking distance.
